{
  "58043": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>呵呵。你已经不行了吗？\n嗯？赞库罗尼<heart><stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58044": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>哈哈<heart>我就知道你会来救他！\n不过很遗～憾！中了那个魔法阵之后，\n靠自己的力量是动不了的。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58045": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>赞库罗尼，这下你算是穷途末路了。\n这么弱还敢说自己是英雄，笑死人了。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58046": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>魔女格雷策尔……\n我可以把命给你。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58047": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>所以你就不要再折磨\n梅尔桑蒂村的村民们了。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58048": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>………………才不要～<heart><stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58049": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>梅尔桑蒂村、梅尔桑蒂村……\n你不顾自己的安危，\n无论如何也要救那个破村子啊……<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58050": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>那为什么……那个时候，\n你没有救我？<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58051": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>你是…………<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58052": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>我现在就帮你结束你的英雄游戏。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58053": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>赞库罗尼……去死吧。<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58054": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>大英雄<heart>\n让你最喜欢的村民把你切个粉碎，\n永远地沉睡吧。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58055": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>拉斯卡……<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58056": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>对不起……我没能救你。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58057": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>哈哈哈哈哈哈！\n居然会被挚爱的村民杀掉，好悲～惨<heart>\n希望什么的根本就不存在。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58058": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>……不对。<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58059": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>无论何时……希望都不会消失。<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58060": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>怎么会……居然挣脱了我的魔法？！<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58061": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>……只要你还能发出声音\n就一定会得救……确实没错。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58062": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>谢谢，拉斯卡。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58063": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>我现在只能做到这些了……\n你去打倒魔女吧……<cs_pchero>。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58064": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>……好啊。\n就让我亲手结束这个英雄的故事吧。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58065": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>没有什么奇迹，血和泪也早就已经干了。\n让你们见识一下什么是真正的结束。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58066": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>就让我亲手结束这个英雄的故事吧。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58067": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>没有什么奇迹，血和泪也早就已经干了。\n让你们见识一下什么是真正的结束。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58068": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>赞库罗尼大人！<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58069": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>真是对不住啊，拉斯卡。\n还要让你来救我。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58070": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>魔女啊……你为什么会恨我？\n为什么要破坏村子，扰乱村民们的生活？<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58071": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>你为什么会变成这样？<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58072": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>……克蕾尔。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58073": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>……你发现了啊。\n算了。就在最后跟你说说往事吧。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58074": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>那是遥远的过去……\n梅尔桑蒂村比现在更加贫困，\n一直受到怪物的威胁……<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "90132": {
    "<center>是魔女！": ""
  },
  "58075": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>在梅尔桑蒂村有个小女孩\n被村民们称作魔女的女儿，\n一直遭人虐待。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58076": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>那个女孩就是我。\n因为我过世的祖母\n会使用神奇的法术。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58077": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>在村里无处安身的我以为只要\n村子富裕起来，就不会再有人虐待我了。\n于是我去向祠堂里的精灵大人祈祷。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58078": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>就在那时，英雄赞库罗尼出现了。\n我记得你击退了袭击村子的怪物，\n被大家捧上了天。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58079": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>虽然村里人都没有发现，\n但我马上就认出了你。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58080": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>你就是祠堂里的精灵大人。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58081": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>但是……怪物还是一直袭击村子。\n然后村子里就出现了奇怪的传闻。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58082": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>传闻说……是魔女\n召来了怪物。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58083": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>传闻慢慢在村里传开了，\n不久后所有人都相信了这个传闻。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58084": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>我本希望能和你逃去很远的地方，\n但我的愿望并没有实现……<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58085": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>在你这个大英雄不知道的地方，\n村民们把我抓起来，\n对我百般辱骂。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58086": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>我好不容易逃了出来，\n跑啊跑啊……但还是被追上了，\n掉进了深深的山谷里。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58087": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>遍体鳞伤，心灰意冷的女孩\n在死亡的深渊里憎恨英雄，诅咒村子……\n变成了真正的魔女。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "93317": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>这就是发生在１００年前的\n梅尔桑蒂村的故事。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58088": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>可喜可贺，可喜可贺<heart><stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58089": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>所以你就袭击\n梅尔桑蒂村？<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58090": {
    "<start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>……没错。<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58091": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>你真是没救了。\n就算你再恨过去的梅尔桑蒂村，\n现在的村民们也是无辜的。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58092": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>不管有什么理由，\n你做的事都是不对的。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58093": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>等等，赞库罗尼大人！<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58094": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>这个人真的可以杀掉吗？<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58095": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>……拉斯卡。\n你觉得英雄最需要的是什么？<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58096": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>厚脸皮！<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58097": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>没错。你记得很清楚嘛。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58098": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>梅尔桑蒂村所有的悲剧\n都是源自我的罪孽。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58099": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>所以就由我来厚着脸皮\n解决这一切吧。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58100": {
    "<shake_camera 40><start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>你的怨恨……我来承担。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58101": {
    "<shake_camera 40><start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>你……你竟然做出这种事情！<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58102": {
    "<shake_camera 40><start_lip_sync m50180 _normal m00001>住手，赞库罗尼！\n如果吸收了我身上的污秽，\n你这个精灵就会消失！<stop_lip_animation m50180 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58103": {
    "<shake_camera 40><start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>我一直在后悔。\n后悔自己没能救你……<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58104": {
    "<shake_camera 40><start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>我不会让你死的。\n你要拼命地活下去赎罪。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58105": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02228 _normal m00001>你这个男人真是蠢透了……<stop_lip_animation n02228 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58106": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>赞库罗尼大人！你的身体！<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58107": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>拉斯卡，我有件事拜托你。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58108": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>我已经无法保护梅尔桑蒂村了。\n你来代替我保护村子吧。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "100771": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>克蕾尔就……拜托你了。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58109": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>……我知道了。交给我吧。<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58110": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001><cs_pchero>，对你我可真是\n感激不尽啊。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58111": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>我会记住你对我的帮助，好搭档。\n能遇见你真是太好了。<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58112": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02090 _normal m00001>无论什么时候都不能舍弃希望。\n梅尔桑蒂村……与我……同在……<stop_lip_animation n02090 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58113": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02228 _normal m00001>赞库罗尼……<stop_lip_animation n02228 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58114": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>你今后活着一定会比\n死了还要痛苦。<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58115": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>被村民们谴责，甚至被打，\n也是没有办法的事。<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58116": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>即使这样也要坚强地活下去。\n我会保护你的，\n因为这是赞库罗尼大人的愿望。<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58117": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02228 _normal m00001>谢谢你……拉斯卡。<stop_lip_animation n02228 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58118": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>嗯，就交给我吧！\n只要你还能发出声音就一定会得救！<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58119": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02002 _normal m00001>那就回梅尔桑蒂村吧！<stop_lip_animation n02002 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58120": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02212 _normal m00001><pc>！\n我一直在等你。<stop_lip_animation n02212 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58121": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02212 _normal m00001>《小英雄赞库罗尼的故事》的结局\n我终于写完了。<stop_lip_animation n02212 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58122": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02212 _normal m00001>我们说好的，你要成为我的第一个读者。<stop_lip_animation n02212 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58123": {
    "<center>……赞库罗尼就这样\n承受着所有的怨恨\n消失不见了。": ""
  },
  "58124": {
    "<center>变回人类的克蕾尔\n一直在梅尔桑蒂村为村民们工作，\n她的真诚终于感动了村民们的心。": ""
  },
  "58125": {
    "<center>梅尔桑蒂村已经没有英雄了。\n但是那颗心\n永远与村子同在。": ""
  },
  "58126": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02212 _normal m00001>谢谢你愿意读我写的故事。\n<pc>……<stop_lip_animation n02212 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58127": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02212 _normal m00001>我看了爷爷的笔记本，\n心头的阴云一下子就消失不见了，\n故事写得特别顺利。<stop_lip_animation n02212 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58128": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02212 _normal m00001>但是我还是没有自信……\n这样的结局真的好吗？<stop_lip_animation n02212 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58129": {
    "要把庞帕尼涅的口信\n告诉爱丽吗？<yesno><close>": ""
  },
  "58132": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02212 _normal m00001>诶？\n庞帕尼涅爷爷说\n他感谢我？<stop_lip_animation n02212 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58133": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02212 _normal m00001><pc>这么说的话，\n就一定是真的。<stop_lip_animation n02212 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58134": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02212 _normal m00001>这个结局很好吧。\n爷爷……<stop_lip_animation n02212 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58130": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02212 _normal m00001>那个……<pc>，\n你不说话我就更担心了。<stop_lip_animation n02212 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58131": {
    "要把庞帕尼涅的口信\n告诉爱丽吗？<yesno><close>": ""
  },
  "58135": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02212 _normal m00001>多亏了你我才实现了梦想。\n如果没有<pc>你的话，\n小英雄的故事也不可能写到结局吧。<stop_lip_animation n02212 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "58136": {
    "<start_lip_sync n02212 _normal m00001>我打心底里感谢你。\n谢谢你……不可思议的旅行者！<stop_lip_animation n02212 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  }
